te><blockquote>如果你想cut線而人地去緊，應該係閃你唔好cut住<br />\n有時閃你可能提你冇開燈，你㗎車有問題等等<br />\n其實冇話有咩好特定嘅意思，我唔鍾意呠人，多數都係閃下高燈算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係叫你唔好CUT 直頭應該砵鳩你</blockquote><br />\n砵你係應該太急姐，有時唔知佢cut定唔cut嘅，我都會閃下佢，等佢唔好阻住"},{"pid":"8f8757d2123bcd48e5520594d820a9085bbdca7b","tid":145390,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性暗示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fbf9b1c7bcac434b750cc6df08862040bdc205","tid":145390,"uid":39642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對頭閃兩下代表前面有相機RB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好窩心既溫馨提示</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個都有聽聞過....我都好想經歷下呢種窩心提示"},{"pid":"cd01450f5ab486d9f2ddac5499c23d45469f2e7b","tid":145390,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0291b2c15338fd87fe870e7118cd931ba033db7","tid":145390,"uid":39642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>性暗示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08551d51df9a53cbcd02467da1c795e9df153ee","tid":145390,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6514d266a98ef762bf55ab9fe2eaa86da2ebd600","tid":145390,"uid":39642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你打住燈人地高燈閃你應該就係讓你叫你出，如果行住直線佢閃你就啫係屌你阻住哂（呢啲人可以繼續頂住佢，除非你霸住快線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好驚俾人推尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec789c0e974963be7257d56ee50907821e9dc23f","tid":145390,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"幾搞笑<br />\n冇車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a075388d430534aec0fff74c1a8b70a25c82e5","tid":145390,"uid":51037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"讓尻你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848ca221032dac3bc40222f85298c8f4a0e8925b","tid":145390,"uid":4209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:04:27.000Z","msg":"即係「要過就快撚啲啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"52e94ef5c5b0d228b859b4ef8b87687be28a60f1","tid":145390,"uid":35640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"閃兩下咪讓你出囉"},{"pid":"9821e7b0d3cc86f24f4e25ee480448c2eeb30380","tid":145390,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排渣車時 想cut 線 打了右燈，跟住後面架車閃兩下高燈，因為小弟岩岩甩p 無耐所以果陣唔敢出 。後尾問fd ，佢話係讓我，但上某d fb 群組又見到 有人話閃兩下高燈係話俾人聽 危險唔好出。<br />\n<br />\n想問車台巴絲有咩高見？同埋仲有冇咩道路上既默認左既燈號？<br />\n<br />\n利伸：掛p 期間 一直有渣車，最後無任何意外</blockquote><br />\n叫你出呀"},{"pid":"8e3cd3d848a72c18e5463655e5d54ec664ed95cb","tid":145390,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開大燈射你=好撚憎你<br />\n<br />\n打死火燈比後面睇=唔該你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打死火燈=唔該，唔係日本先係咁問？</blockquote><br />\n日本都唔係架架車會，但巴士就99％都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大部分九巴都會"},{"pid":"91399f6177eca7a83b3656eff8cfd3fa19ef3914","tid":145390,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:08:34.000Z","msg":"初頭甩P我都試過同樣情況, 又係有人同過我講佢收慢閃你即係讓你cut, <br />\n有一次比架的士狗無啦啦停車等客頂住我, 咁我就打右燈準備cut啦, <br />\n當時都係驚驚地因為唔係揸左好耐, 等咗5架車過哂喇, <br />\n後面有架中港牌寶馬就仲有段距離, 佢閃左兩下又收慢, 咁我咪出, <br />\n點知佢條撚樣即刻篤油加狂呠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我架車已經出咗一半, <br />\n最後係變左3架車平排, 好彩我之前架車仔細冇hi到...佢過左之後仲要屌哂老母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n果陣因為唔熟呢啲嘢...係咁講唔好意思, 其實個心諗你唔想讓你咪照比油去囉, <br />\n又收哂又閃燈咁做乜..."},{"pid":"9e28e4d2aa968e243c08d31a429fa6fa6cde0bc2","tid":145390,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"想同你鍊車"},{"pid":"2f0777b7ceaa47c728fbf2d87787eb7c4ad2ca53","tid":145390,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"打死火燈商業車用<br />\n私家車好少打死火燈講唔該"},{"pid":"ea834f741c3bdaa8b4389a953e028c7dea5959be","tid":145390,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"成日係街見到人唔開燈, 我都閃下佢, 但係佢又唔理我"},{"pid":"570c204b957857a108653fde95f295455b4f5bec","tid":145390,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:11:17.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n<br />\n之前我想cut右線 <br />\n後面架貨車接近停係到咁閃兩下高燈<br />\n我見佢咁慢就直接cut<br />\n但我老豆話警告緊"},{"pid":"389db1948565fc4f2a6c1065d19f4771df23b31d","tid":145390,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對頭閃兩下代表前面有相機RB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好窩心既溫馨提示</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個都有聽聞過....我都好想經歷下呢種窩心提示</blockquote><br />\n成日經歷，所以我都會閃番人</blockquote><br />\n你點知對頭係閃緊你<br />\n定閃比佢前面叫佢cut線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d38229afa972c9680eb73ed5b987e4d9616cae6","tid":145390,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日係街見到人唔開燈, 我都閃下佢, 但係佢又唔理我</blockquote><br />\n佢其實係架車入面講緊<br />\n屌你老母閃乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過"},{"pid":"ee7b5701f0ddff5de112eae71e92754d20b9325e","tid":145390,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想同你鍊車</blockquote><br />\n讓又有唔讓又有<br />\n最似就你呢個答案"},{"pid":"8caf58b480e09c20c76ceb2ac0b7c5f8a1f2a658","tid":145390,"uid":35839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:15:36.000Z","msg":"甩P半年，知晒樓上講嗰啲意思，但都想問，有時見有road block 想閃對面線，又驚自己線前車以為我閃（屌）尻佢，你地會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想提人冇開燈又係，閃佢好似屌佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好混淆求教，點唔令人get錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4522b931d343e2253c048940313443bd3d6dfd0b","tid":145390,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甩P半年，知晒樓上講嗰啲意思，但都想問，有時見有road block 想閃對面線，又驚自己線前車以為我閃（屌）尻佢，你地會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想提人冇開燈又係，閃佢好似屌佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好混淆求教，點唔令人get錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開咪同佢講"},{"pid":"c6b673147c0fe6eea6f0729de234780f2ad846f8","tid":145390,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"夜晚有d車無開燈行<br />\n千祈咪閃/o本佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各有各行算啦"},{"pid":"a02c045ca23bc7b12ab653d0a4b83ed48c9ed72c","tid":145390,"uid":18944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"試過想cut 線  隔離線巴士佬閃一下+收油比我出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d736a10efb946b0bc2e27393d1911f4943b89530","tid":145390,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甩P半年，知晒樓上講嗰啲意思，但都想問，有時見有road block 想閃對面線，又驚自己線前車以為我閃（屌）尻佢，你地會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想提人冇開燈又係，閃佢好似屌佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好混淆求教，點唔令人get錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得想提佢有Road block閃到爆都冇事, 因為就算當下佢覺得你係閃尻佢都好, 佢見到個block就會知你用意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35629c4beb31ff0b9de4a2a77ff509e5dcec6ca","tid":145390,"uid":39642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對頭閃兩下代表前面有相機RB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好窩心既溫馨提示</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個都有聽聞過....我都好想經歷下呢種窩心提示</blockquote><br />\n成日經歷，所以我都會閃番人</blockquote><br />\n你點知對頭係閃緊你<br />\n定閃比佢前面叫佢cut線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n突破盲腸"},{"pid":"fce3618d434cd24b3bf5fb3d279e0e752257c54b","tid":145390,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甩P半年，知晒樓上講嗰啲意思，但都想問，有時見有road block 想閃對面線，又驚自己線前車以為我閃（屌）尻佢，你地會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想提人冇開燈又係，閃佢好似屌佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好混淆求教，點唔令人get錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBlock呢d睇情況啦，前車遠既話都唔會誤會到既其實<br />\n<br />\n無開燈你閃兩下佢知就知唔知就算<br />\n通常俾人閃會醒一醒諗下有咩事"},{"pid":"2c6e46d9b1f115f1582736dea828e3dc89cdf9a9","tid":145390,"uid":32252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打死火燈商業車用<br />\n私家車好少打死火燈講唔該</blockquote><br />\n我會打死火燈講唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2f304047c72d6292d71b5830b6a0b22fd32124","tid":145390,"uid":39642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初頭甩P我都試過同樣情況, 又係有人同過我講佢收慢閃你即係讓你cut, <br />\n有一次比架的士狗無啦啦停車等客頂住我, 咁我就打右燈準備cut啦, <br />\n當時都係驚驚地因為唔係揸左好耐, 等咗5架車過哂喇, <br />\n後面有架中港牌寶馬就仲有段距離, 佢閃左兩下又收慢, 咁我咪出, <br />\n點知佢條撚樣即刻篤油加狂呠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我架車已經出咗一半, <br />\n最後係變左3架車平排, 好彩我之前架車仔細冇hi到...佢過左之後仲要屌哂老母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n果陣因為唔熟呢啲嘢...係咁講唔好意思, 其實個心諗你唔想讓你咪照比油去囉, <br />\n又收哂又閃燈咁做乜...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係撞左，邊個唔著？"},{"pid":"ac06085465261eaee5e36df2d07f54b618afef25","tid":145390,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>初頭甩P我都試過同樣情況, 又係有人同過我講佢收慢閃你即係讓你cut, <br />\n有一次比架的士狗無啦啦停車等客頂住我, 咁我就打右燈準備cut啦, <br />\n當時都係驚驚地因為唔係揸左好耐, 等咗5架車過哂喇, <br />\n後面有架<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中港牌</span></span>寶馬就仲有段距離, 佢閃左兩下又收慢, 咁我咪出, <br />\n點知佢條撚樣即刻篤油加狂呠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我架車已經出咗一半, <br />\n最後係變左3架車平排, 好彩我之前架車仔細冇hi到...佢過左之後仲要屌哂老母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n果陣因為唔熟呢啲嘢...係咁講唔好意思, 其實個心諗你唔想讓你咪照比油去囉, <br />\n又收哂又閃燈咁做乜...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係撞左，邊個唔著？</blockquote><br />\n你"},{"pid":"3d2d716cd098d3ce8c0ce56f59a9767404def913","tid":145390,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:24:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54e493366d90b00bc68fbd6a5a660017cc7e9c44","tid":145390,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"揸多d你留意下其他車動態<br />\n你自然會意會得到<br />\n如果一地收慢讓你就快快手出<br />\n如果唔係就算人地唔開窗屌鳩你一樣會係內心入邊屌柒你"},{"pid":"4a9023c4bdd319d16208435fbe11a0aea7ec640d","tid":145390,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開大燈射你=好撚憎你<br />\n<br />\n打死火燈比後面睇=唔該你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打死火燈=唔該，唔係日本先係咁問？</blockquote><br />\n大嶼山都係咁"},{"pid":"f670a5ce256e8b1c3a1ccace2903977bda7acb2c","tid":145390,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>初頭甩P我都試過同樣情況, 又係有人同過我講佢收慢閃你即係讓你cut, <br />\n有一次比架的士狗無啦啦停車等客頂住我, 咁我就打右燈準備cut啦, <br />\n當時都係驚驚地因為唔係揸左好耐, 等咗5架車過哂喇, <br />\n後面有架中港牌寶馬就仲有段距離, 佢閃左兩下又收慢, 咁我咪出, <br />\n點知佢條撚樣即刻篤油加狂呠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我架車已經出咗一半, <br />\n最後係變左3架車平排, 好彩我之前架車仔細冇hi到...佢過左之後仲要屌哂老母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n果陣因為唔熟呢啲嘢...係咁講唔好意思, 其實個心諗你唔想讓你咪照比油去囉, <br />\n又收哂又閃燈咁做乜...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係撞左，邊個唔著？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該都係入我 (其實我有後車cam), 所以嗰次之後人地點閃都好我都唔會咁輕易信佢, 理得佢閃係讓我定屌我唔好出住都好, <br />\n自己睇清楚cut得, 安全就去, 好似呢個情況如果我等埋架車過埋先cut 就冇時, <br />\n問番邊個啱邊個錯就好難講... 但條友冇品就一定架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9ff35548ab510bc7696f0d63b9b53d4264bee1","tid":145390,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁閃兩下連登又係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈哈哈哈"},{"pid":"be991947771fcbbc1e8ecf07f79a393e76071cfe","tid":145390,"uid":31963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閃兩下=叫你條仆街快d cut過黎<br />\n狂閃=叫你咪撚過<br />\n咇你=屌你老母<br />\n雙程線，對面迎頭車閃=你前面有路障/捉超速/撞車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全中"},{"pid":"2f02557f9587efb4249266debc33c6cf43250d03","tid":145390,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"自己習慣<br />\n受人恩惠 =兩下死火燈<br />\n讓人／提人開車=兩閃大燈<br />\n提人開頭燈=熄頭燈再開"},{"pid":"72cad87ec373fa0bc4c3dac7c4f42573ca299d35","tid":145390,"uid":81264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>閃兩下=叫你條仆街快d cut過黎<br />\n狂閃=叫你咪撚過<br />\n咇你=屌你老母<br />\n雙程線，對面迎頭車閃=你前面有路障/捉超速/撞車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全中</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n以前想讓但唔知手快快狂閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無車出黎"},{"pid":"7e9416083c3a58a189c4e3c6625c601b35b6611b","tid":145390,"uid":39642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己習慣<br />\n受人恩惠 =兩下死火燈<br />\n讓人／提人開車=兩閃大燈<br />\n提人開頭燈=熄頭燈再開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你果個提開頭燈 既方法 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc605d656ea973a759bba58627fa1e5052e0749","tid":145390,"uid":33908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己習慣<br />\n受人恩惠 =兩下死火燈<br />\n讓人／提人開車=兩閃大燈<br />\n提人開頭燈=熄頭燈再開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你果個提開頭燈 既方法 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遇著黑警會唔會整張唔開燈黎嘆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859aece3bc9953382b61b4d60149bb3ed0c7af8c","tid":145390,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己習慣<br />\n受人恩惠 =兩下死火燈<br />\n讓人／提人開車=兩閃大燈<br />\n提人開頭燈=熄頭燈再開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你果個提開頭燈 既方法 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係...<br />\n<br />\n多謝 = 三下死火燈+係倒後鏡前提起手 / cut 線的話開窗提手<br />\n讓人行先 = 閃兩下大燈再收慢<br />\n提人開頭燈 = 閃兩下大燈...關頭燈再重開頭燈<br />\n提人關死火燈 = 閃兩下大燈再打五下死火燈再閃兩下大燈<br />\n<br />\n問候人地亂咁楂車 = 直接呠佢兩野再係車入面鬧啦...."},{"pid":"74419400f83ea1bccaf3e5fa1dba057a3cb412d0","tid":145390,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"見佢收慢咪即係讓你"},{"pid":"af3bb8ee05e4209c22f668c57adea56876e16191","tid":145390,"uid":83058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"試過人地閃兩下收慢讓我出，之後我出完打死火燈講多謝，佢即刻咇爆我仲沖上泥話讓你出仲玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194de9dba134c64f41b0c4a55b0f191c74fbae86","tid":145390,"uid":68837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己習慣<br />\n受人恩惠 =兩下死火燈<br />\n讓人／提人開車=兩閃大燈<br />\n提人開頭燈=熄頭燈再開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你果個提開頭燈 既方法 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係...<br />\n<br />\n多謝 = 三下死火燈+係倒後鏡前提起手 / cut 線的話開窗提手<br />\n讓人行先 = 閃兩下大燈再收慢<br />\n提人開頭燈 = 閃兩下大燈...關頭燈再重開頭燈<br />\n提人關死火燈 = 閃兩下大燈再打五下死火燈再閃兩下大燈<br />\n<br />\n問候人地亂咁楂車 = 直接呠佢兩野再係車入面鬧啦....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁複雜 你爭在未用大燈打摩斯密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e958043ba9be548b48b6a99c239cc67d56747f","tid":145390,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過人地閃兩下收慢讓我出，之後我出完打死火燈講多謝，佢即刻咇爆我仲沖上泥話讓你出仲玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw<br />\n泥你....."},{"pid":"ad6932faa062cc5889e3bb0525e0ede13490b2c1","tid":145390,"uid":38405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"閃兩下-入啦仆街<br />\n喪閃-屌你老味咪撚嚟呀你<br />\n死火燈-唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對面線閃燈-前面有快相"},{"pid":"6d4fa01f85d1cc4f8709ce1187aae35d4f5edee3","tid":145390,"uid":6537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對頭閃兩下代表前面有相機RB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好窩心既溫馨提示</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個都有聽聞過....我都好想經歷下呢種窩心提示</blockquote><br />\n入將軍澳工業村經常會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178b6761150ac0dda01519e84d0c983d24574314","tid":145390,"uid":5827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打死火燈商業車用<br />\n私家車好少打死火燈講唔該</blockquote><br />\n真係死火又死火燈 唔該又死火燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"3a8ffda2181bf780b94e544b11e5fd8e11c7f9f6","tid":145390,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打死火燈商業車用<br />\n私家車好少打死火燈講唔該</blockquote><br />\n真係死火又死火燈 唔該又死火燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n我會追上前閘停佢再落車講唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都係一種訊號<br />\n個個都用<br />\n就會變共同語言<br />\n而且死火係長閃<br />\n多謝只係閃幾下就停"},{"pid":"657710e7f54a6f5ce25c77ed049d3eb870c05f13","tid":145390,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"差d以為個post係我開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n閃大燈真係好高深, 同好嚇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np牌中, 有時慢線係出口, <br />\n咁唯有cut去中線, <br />\n一打燈準備中既時候,<br />\n中線d車就會閃兩下大燈, <br />\n其實我睇到你架, 我只係想話你知我想cut咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果下次次都唔知佢想屌鬼我小心d咪亂cut定讓俾我cut,<br />\n我會定油睇定d佢係收油定篤油再決定幾時cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948d6562628d252337098ec9c27c47079fe9a2f2","tid":145390,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打死火燈商業車用<br />\n私家車好少打死火燈講唔該</blockquote><br />\n真係死火又死火燈 唔該又死火燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該只係打兩至三下....<br />\n如果係高速公路真係慢車 / 前面有死車就會 keep 住打啦..."},{"pid":"568cf5669cdbc268741fdbc5382b69c15fb944d8","tid":145390,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對頭閃兩下代表前面有相機RB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"5f10c6ab0e12298deaa2b4eb751c8d1fcb657985","tid":145390,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:36:41.000Z","msg":"根據頭D定律<br />\n佢閃完你<br />\n你一係收油泊埋一邊唔好阻住人<br />\n一係就唔好俾佢見到你車尾燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b3a2c416fb21aa5cd1d9015d63439aa14db972","tid":145390,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:38:37.000Z","msg":"叫你cut 呀傻鳩"},{"pid":"c96fcb0a8dfaf9f03b34cc7f1a417770304b9478","tid":145390,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"咪掛住上連登"},{"pid":"03efc3d728fcfdb76f7587e10636cba6eac6a089","tid":145390,"uid":12303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"Roadblock"},{"pid":"a2bbcad2446cd4ac63d4635951a6180d61a03c63","tid":145390,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:17:16.000Z","msg":"通常我係閃比人CUT , 比人出"},{"pid":"0d00914d751a3f4735469fd6b7177cd9c3aaea25","tid":145390,"uid":2673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"乜啲嘢自己睇埋車速執生啦，邊有統一做法㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。下面呢條片就係講人哋閃你都咪撚信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1--Qf-ZYtfg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1--Qf-ZYtfg&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ec52f9d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1--Qf-ZYtfg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真有心想讓人嘅你調節吓個車速，多數都會醒目識出...我自己就通常再慢閃一、兩吓高燈，未試過有誤會。夜晚揸我會將個大燈開熄開熄兩吓(或者熄大燈再閃慢閃一兩吓高燈），好清晰唔會有誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b19dee27023ef0e548be42a8a57cd34a7462c4","tid":145390,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"點解我見親閃燈果D 都係比油唔比你去既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c44926814aecdd6e073b0ad2be4fa00a54a133","tid":145390,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:59:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f433c853489b9d42b91daf0b2cad9039c0daa635","tid":145390,"uid":48724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79358ad2c1705a66d785730136e17b3f90776382","tid":145390,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"係唔係撚過架 屌你老母快啦<br />\n咁<br />\n唔想你過就油門響按 撞我賠錢架屌你老母架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋啱啱過完線咪撚死火 陣間後面急停連環炒車就真係多撚謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43f53083aed8bedced144e97d1c8e8d8a02ee99","tid":145390,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:32:29.000Z","msg":"後面閃你得一個原因就係催你快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對面線離遠閃你通常就係收油讓你，你就好醒水拿拿聲岀加比返隻手人講唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行公路對面線啲車，尤其搵食車閃就係提你前面有相機自己小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa09b8925bf5d90adc1c6592eb579e37142a181","tid":145390,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閃兩下連燈咩意思？</blockquote><br />\n閃一下 = 高燈<br />\n閃兩下 = 連燈<br />\n狂閃 = 連住尼閃"},{"pid":"8b90a33b2c537a2d3af2acb57d5cf5563a0f6ee1","tid":145390,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>閃兩下連燈咩意思？</blockquote><br />\n閃一下 = 高燈<br />\n閃兩下 = 連燈<br />\n狂閃 = 連住尼閃</blockquote><br />\n睇錯連尼住"},{"pid":"a462784eac7d0a0012e0f54991613ff47a60d6ae","tid":145390,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過人地閃兩下收慢讓我出，之後我出完打死火燈講多謝，佢即刻咇爆我仲沖上泥話讓你出仲玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泥你老..<br />\n我個人 讓就一下 提醒警告就兩下 硬cut我既就長開jer住佢"},{"pid":"8c005d0ff33218acf72a89e0eedf98df441b94e1","tid":145390,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:19:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過人地閃兩下收慢讓我出，之後我出完打死火燈講多謝，佢即刻咇爆我仲沖上泥話讓你出仲玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泥你老..<br />\n我個人 讓就一下 提醒警告就兩下 硬cut我既就長開jer住佢</blockquote><br />\n唔讓閃嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪Keep住啖油直行直過，係又閃唔係又閃，對方又唔知你想點以為叫你一嘢岀隊岀嚟就碌柒啦開追悼會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badd4959d597dfc8c5bac7532f23823bae36a593","tid":145390,"uid":34889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開大燈射你=好撚憎你<br />\n<br />\n打死火燈比後面睇=唔該你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打死火燈=唔該，唔係日本先係咁問？</blockquote><br />\n我都會咁做, 喺台灣都見過"},{"pid":"eba538e981f713633e70db5d4a8ef6768c7e27de","tid":145390,"uid":37259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"琴晚響加士居道天橋，對頭線有架的士閃左兩下高燈<br />\n可能又係前面例牌位 bbq 啦，有冇 bbq 就真係唔知<br />\n首先我係果欄已經落左橋<br />\n第二就係我架車頭右邊大燈燒左剩係著得細燈<br />\n所以我都唔知佢真正想提我 d 咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44b15c5f43cb431b1b3b0e4cb848470f6b72cf5","tid":145390,"uid":26422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"閃高燈=有野同你講<br />\n想知佢講咩咪望下鏡留意下囉<br />\n其實未必係上述咁多個意思"},{"pid":"3e4c9a8ee99f3ebec5efb3b63e848addf6a0c7b1","tid":145390,"uid":48724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4543f44b6d44bf9b593f6ddb3f5a6067ab2f8e0","tid":145390,"uid":48724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:46:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c342da2d3d6ed7a11ebcac9ace634a71b7fe659","tid":145390,"uid":3217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"佢收就係叫你出<br />\n佢快你就讓開比佢"},{"pid":"5a10da436cf7556ee8840125b8e699006f78d55f","tid":145390,"uid":8349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:12:27.000Z","msg":"快車+閃=咪撚出<br />\n慢車+閃=讓你"},{"pid":"60a3b14031296711771569cd8ec75e6b66f26561","tid":145390,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快車+閃=咪撚出<br />\n慢車+閃=讓你</blockquote><br />\n結論： 閃=多鳩餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168ba50ed1fa9669fcced64cc1f12b704109d329","tid":145390,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T19:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試過人地閃兩下收慢讓我出，之後我出完打死火燈講多謝，佢即刻咇爆我仲沖上泥話讓你出仲玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泥你老..<br />\n我個人 讓就一下 提醒警告就兩下 硬cut我既就長開jer住佢</blockquote><br />\n唔讓閃嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪Keep住啖油直行直過，係又閃唔係又閃，對方又唔知你想點以為叫你一嘢岀隊岀嚟就碌柒啦開追悼會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁就緊係收左油先閃佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想佢出就快閃"},{"pid":"13010079c966564730e5d7643f955159a5ffbd1d","tid":145390,"uid":57584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:08:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d7882f5eb2283805cbcc2f54c944674ebd0a2b2","tid":145390,"uid":54276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:13:55.000Z","msg":"其實閃你即係叫你留意，望撚住啦咁姐，佢有無意讓你其實睇得出嘅"},{"pid":"e339f689712dac7df066bb92045f7a273d624cfa","tid":145390,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:20:49.000Z","msg":"打死火燈講唔該唔戇鳩"},{"pid":"f87331d25fee1d8de52dbe263c2d152956d8494e","tid":145390,"uid":73696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:15:15.000Z","msg":"對面線提你有快相通常都係 呠呠呠呠～呠呠 好有節奏"},{"pid":"d73f706fb00b5785a601532b11f8065724589b09","tid":145390,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對面線提你有快相通常都係 呠呠呠呠～呠呠 好有節奏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未聽過&hellip;係真唔係呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360d585ba8db32ec4273c33f3213757dfc00a5b6","tid":145390,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對面線提你有快相通常都係 呠呠呠呠～呠呠 好有節奏</blockquote><br />\n唔係多數閃2下高燈咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己提對面線都係咁做"},{"pid":"bf192c4688abd29610fddc823a7d2c2aaa9abd44","tid":145390,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"我留意到你想cut線，快啲出<br />\n如果揸得好衰有危險我多數呠佢，果啲人柒下柒下閃佢都睇唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0f8783e77b4ee253762991f5f392a7f93b219f","tid":145390,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"其實佢閃唔閃都好<br />\n正路睇倒鏡睇車速就知佢讓唔讓你<br />\n閃你嘅話你就望一望佢係真心定假膠"},{"pid":"311f88076cee3e9d724ae1813c394f8c65d2f1df","tid":145390,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對面線提你有快相通常都係 呠呠呠呠～呠呠 好有節奏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n亂響安小心有龜車抽閘你再320呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f59cae4d43d6e7155a7edbc794ceda5ea28a73f","tid":145390,"uid":29592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:15:20.000Z","msg":"返屋企有一段山路限速70 經常有啲撚屌行40/50 究竟有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後面排哂隊都好 撚屌們一直行40/50 又唔入避車處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686a843d9cd16a108a3af26a3032ad1e714ae910","tid":145390,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返屋企有一段山路限速70 經常有啲撚屌行40/50 究竟有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後面排哂隊都好 撚屌們一直行40/50 又唔入避車處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n閃撚佢推撚佢呠撚佢"},{"pid":"99524a2294d8bea6856de87e974f307cb625a154","tid":145390,"uid":46979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"如果要多謝人地讓你,<br />\n建議舉手算<br />\n因為香港好多人都唔知打2下死火燈點解<br />\n有d仲以為你串9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有時入停車場或圍村單線雙程路時,<br />\n如果對面/前面有人泊緊車都會熄左車頭燈<br />\n費時俾咁大壓力人"},{"pid":"56363522d669be306881afb705d68cd0da3ed8d1","tid":145390,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"你點知對頭閃你定閃佢前面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e885002904d21b881b1526572daac8a1581f2c41","tid":145390,"uid":15339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己習慣<br />\n受人恩惠 =兩下死火燈<br />\n讓人／提人開車=兩閃大燈<br />\n提人開頭燈=熄頭燈再開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你果個提開頭燈 既方法 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係...<br />\n<br />\n多謝 = 三下死火燈+係倒後鏡前提起手 / cut 線的話開窗提手<br />\n讓人行先 = 閃兩下大燈再收慢<br />\n提人開頭燈 = 閃兩下大燈...關頭燈再重開頭燈<br />\n提人關死火燈 = 閃兩下大燈再打五下死火燈再閃兩下大燈<br />\n<br />\n問候人地亂咁楂車 = 直接呠佢兩野再係車入面鬧啦....</blockquote><br />\n你揸車個時都幾忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c44f32d46f342d8c43f2eae1293cabb3583797d","tid":145390,"uid":65408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"車與車之間原來有咁多信息要溝通，點解冇人發明emoji燈去方便表達意思？<br />\n🖕👍👌🙇🏻"},{"pid":"7ffbac1ab3d9bbc53dbf05f5292e1970f6374905","tid":145390,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"車入面擺多兩盞燈仔(i.e. 一紅一綠) , 自己做一套訊號可行性高唔高?"},{"pid":"f70ee3c2b50990a912970becf74ac3f5ba914f76","tid":145390,"uid":39642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>車入面擺多兩盞燈仔(i.e. 一紅一綠) , 自己做一套訊號可行性高唔高?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如 紅同藍 著左 可能可以暢通無阻"},{"pid":"629c6aaf7cdf1da502d234c045a41316299024d8","tid":145390,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:19:23.000Z","msg":"多謝=打兩下死火燈呢樣我喺香港一直都唔敢做<br />\n淨係喺日本自駕先會<br />\n香港馬路太多盲閪炸彈同埋燥狂症<br />\n陣間誤會費撚事嘈"},{"pid":"496968bdb7e80b193fec9ebd57f6508b3df1f98a","tid":145390,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝=打兩下死火燈呢樣我喺香港一直都唔敢做<br />\n淨係喺日本自駕先會<br />\n香港馬路太多盲閪炸彈同埋燥狂症<br />\n陣間誤會費撚事嘈</blockquote><br />\n大把巴士佬咁做"},{"pid":"d523c023e243c7aace7ae1da3360ae462da15854","tid":145390,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:27:01.000Z","msg":"閃+收慢=讓你<br />\n閃+俾油=睇路啦仆街<br />\n實際上,閃只係叫你注意,至於注意d乜就自己領會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0624e3aa6ff688533bd23f6e5f03bd1b49cadfd9","tid":145390,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差d以為個post係我開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n閃大燈真係好高深, 同好嚇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np牌中, 有時慢線係出口, <br />\n咁唯有cut去中線, <br />\n一打燈準備中既時候,<br />\n中線d車就會閃兩下大燈, <br />\n其實我睇到你架, 我只係想話你知我想cut咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果下次次都唔知佢想屌鬼我小心d咪亂cut定讓俾我cut,<br />\n我會定油睇定d佢係收油定篤油再決定幾時cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實&hellip;點解你唔cut果下先打燈呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一嚟你長閃,隔離線100%俾油唔俾你出<br />\n二嚟你咁長閃法,人地淨係知你想出囉,時機呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實你想cut線果陣,先貼架車埋去,但係唔好過線住,呢到已經足夠俾隔離線知你想cut線<br />\n然後睇準個空位,打燈之後直接扭軚出,人地見到你打燈扭軚果陣,就算即刻俾油都已經衝唔過,咁就會乖乖地收油俾你出嫁啦"},{"pid":"be1b10ff51aa1d8ef0e8919076d925ddc8ace455","tid":145390,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T19:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>差d以為個post係我開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n閃大燈真係好高深, 同好嚇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np牌中, 有時慢線係出口, <br />\n咁唯有cut去中線, <br />\n一打燈準備中既時候,<br />\n中線d車就會閃兩下大燈, <br />\n其實我睇到你架, 我只係想話你知我想cut咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果下次次都唔知佢想屌鬼我小心d咪亂cut定讓俾我cut,<br />\n我會定油睇定d佢係收油定篤油再決定幾時cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實&hellip;點解你唔cut果下先打燈呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一嚟你長閃,隔離線100%俾油唔俾你出<br />\n二嚟你咁長閃法,人地淨係知你想出囉,時機呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實你想cut線果陣,先貼架車埋去,但係唔好過線住,呢到已經足夠俾隔離線知你想cut線<br />\n然後睇準個空位,打燈之後直接扭軚出,人地見到你打燈扭軚果陣,就算即刻俾油都已經衝唔過,咁就會乖乖地收油俾你出嫁啦</blockquote><br />\ncut個下先打燈&hellip;仲要成大篇理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你返屋企打飛機啦，唔好揸車出街害人<br />\n唔想喺街俾你呢d戇鳩炸彈累撚死<br />\n<br />\nbtw上面話p牌中嗰位巴打<br />\n你呢個先打燈，望人地讓唔讓先再出嘅做法完全正確<br />\n咪聽條撚樣鳩up"}]}